CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775811900
OL,3,CExtra police funding to keep people
OL,4,Csafe where they live, work and worship
OL,6,FIt will go towards Project Servator
OL,7,Fdeployments in Manchester and London,
OL,8,Finvolving specialist officers who are
OL,9,Ftrained to spot suspects who might be
OL,10,Fpreparing to commit serious crimes.
OL,12,FMr Jarvis said: "At a time of
OL,13,Fheightened concern for some
OL,14,Fcommunities, it is vital that we step
OL,15,Fup our support.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
