PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775811900
OL,3,CExtra police funding to keep people
OL,4,Csafe where they live, work and worship
OL,6,F"Project Servator has a proven track
OL,7,Frecord of stopping criminals and
OL,8,Fterrorists through highly visible,
OL,9,Funpredictable deployments that vary in
OL,10,Ftime and location, deterring those
OL,11,Fplanning harm and reassuring the
OL,12,Fpublic.
OL,14,F"This new funding will back the police
OL,15,Fwith the resources they need to step
OL,16,Fup patrols, protect communities, and
OL,17,Fkeep people safe in the places where
OL,18,Fthey live, work and worship."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
