OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775811900
OL,3,CExtra police funding to keep people
OL,4,Csafe where they live, work and worship
OL,6,FAccording to the Home Office, previous
OL,7,FProject Servator deployments have
OL,8,Finvolved both visible uniformed and
OL,9,Fplain clothes officers.
OL,11,FThey have led to arrests and drugs and
OL,12,Fweapons seizures.
OL,14,FThe new effort, which builds on #73.4
OL,15,Fmillion already committed for
OL,16,Fprotective security at Jewish, Muslim
OL,17,Fand other faith sites for 2026-27,
OL,18,Fwill initially focus on policing in
OL,19,Fcommunities, particularly faith
OL,20,Fcommunities, across Manchester and
OL,21,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
