FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1775811900
OL,3,CExtra police funding to keep people
OL,4,Csafe where they live, work and worship
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police Inspector
OL,7,FChris Hadfield said: "Our patrols are
OL,8,Fhighly visible, but deployments are
OL,9,Funpredictable, and can happen at any
OL,10,Ftime, in any given location.
OL,12,F"The teams also regularly conduct
OL,13,Fdeployments in and around local faith
OL,14,Fcommunities, supporting cultural
OL,15,Fevents and holy days.
OL,17,F"It is our aim that this funding will
OL,18,Fcontinue to support this mission and
OL,19,Fensure the public always know the best
OL,20,Fplaces to report any suspicious or
OL,21,Funusual activity."
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@RO]
